(Color online.) Schematic of graphene nanoribbons with two narrowest constrictions. (a) shows a nanoribbon with zigzag edges while (b) shows a nanoribbon with armchair edges. The left and the right regions are semi-infinite pristine nanoribbons acting as leads. The number of atom pairs (
N c
) in the box indicates the width of the constrictions.
